    | ExpandTrackMatches SongId
    | SelectTrackForSong Song SpotifyTrack
    | SendToDevice
    | BasePresetChanged String
    | StartingPresetChanged String
    | UrlChanged Url.Url
    | LinkClicked Browser.UrlRequest


